name: Return to Monke (Toni Carrascosa, Kinsey, Evilee73, SirWhatever)
name_original: Return to Monke (Toni Carrascosa, Kinsey, Evilee73, SirWhatever)
description:
REJECT MODERNITY, RETURN TO MONKE!

  • In a world where you are tired of office work you discover there are magical bananas that can make you return to nature with your real brothers. 
  • Collect all of the bananas and become LE MONKE!
